long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "Fatboy Dream" is a Chrome browser extension featuring an engaging arcade game. In this game, players control a character named Fatboy, who aims to eat as much food as possible while avoiding various obstacles and enemies. The game offers simple yet addictive gameplay with increasing difficulty and vibrant cartoon graphics, making it a great choice for a quick break and entertainment between tasks.
